Class MainFrame

    java.awt.image.ImageObserver, java.awt.MenuContainer, java.io.Serializable, javax.accessibility.Accessible, javax.swing.RootPaneContainer, javax.swing.WindowConstants

    public class MainFrame
extends javax.swing.JFrame
    Class representing the look of the main frame of the application. Extends the JFrame class. Contains MainMenuBar, MainToolbar, StatusBar and MainSplitPane. It is based on the singleton design pattern.
    Author:
    Ivan Divljak, Borko Arsovic, Milan Radeta, Isidora Škulec
